<Body>
    <Title>国家地震局启动一级预案　救援队已集结</Title>
    <ReportTime type="absTime">2008年05月12日16:33</ReportTime>
    <Content>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1">
                    <Participant sid="s1">新华网北京</Participant>
                    <Time tid="t1" type="relTime">5月12日</Time>
                    <Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter>
                </Event>
                <Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent">
                    <Participant sid="s2">中国地震局新闻发言人张宏卫</Participant>
                    <Time type="relTime" tid="t2">12日下午</Time>
                    <Denoter type="statement" did="d2">通报</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e3">针对
                    <Location lid="l3">四川汶川</Location>
                    <Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">地震</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e4">
                    <Participant sid="s4">中国地震局</Participant>已
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d4">启动</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o4">一级预案</Object>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e5">
                    <Participant sid="s5">一支180人的救援队</Participant>已经
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d5">集结</Denoter>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent">据
                    <Participant sid="s6">国家地震台网</Participant>
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d6">测定</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e7">
                    <Time type="relTime" tid="t7">12日14时48分</Time>，
                    <Location lid="l7">四川省汶川县</Location>（温江西北55公里，北纬31．0度，东经103．4度）发生7．8级
                    <Denoter type="emergency" did="d7">地震</Denoter>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e8" type="thoughtevent">
                    <Participant sid="s8">中国地震局新闻发言人张宏卫</Participant>
                    <Denoter type="statement" did="d8">说</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e9">此次
                    <Denoter type="emergency" did="d9">地震</Denoter>
                </Event>强度大，波及面广。
			</Sentence>
			<Sentence>最新测得的震级为7．8级，宁夏、青海、甘肃、河南、山西、陕西、山东、云南、湖南、湖北、上海、重庆等省市均有震感。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e10" type="thoughtevent">
                    <Participant sid="s10">张宏卫</Participant>
                    <Denoter type="statement" did="d10">说</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e11">
                    <Participant sid="s11">中国地震局</Participant>已
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d11">启动</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o11">一级预案</Object>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e12">
                    <Participant sid="s12,s13,s14">一支180的救援队伍</Participant>已经
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d12">集结</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e13">准备
                    <Denoter type="movement" did="d13">开往</Denoter>
                    <Location lid="l13">灾区</Location>
                </Event>
                <Event eid="e14">投入
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d14">救援</Denoter>
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e15">
                    <Object oid="o15">地震造成的人员财产损失</Object>正在进一步
                    <Denoter type="operation" did="d15">统计</Denoter>中
                </Event>。
            </Sentence>
        </Paragraph>
    </Content>
